snippet.title: Cave Hopper Trailer
snippet.description:
Cave Hopper is a puzzle platforming game where you play as a frog and try to escape the dark corridors of a cave!

Download it now on the Google Play Store!
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Froststar.CaveHopper

Social media links:
https://www.instagram.com/froststargames/
https://twitter.com/froststargames

Music from https://www.zapsplat.com
